Temperature: Color temperature in Kelvin of the blackbody illuminant
Intensity: Total energy that the light emits in lux.
InnerConeAngle: Inner cone angle in degrees for a Spotlight.
OuterConeAngle: Outer cone angle in degrees for a Spotlight.
AttenuationRadius: Light visible influence. Works for Pointlight and Spotlight.
SourceRadius: Radius of light source shape. Works for Pointlight and Spotlight.
SoftSourceRadius: Soft radius of light source shape. Works for Pointlight and Spotlight.
SourceLength: Length of light source shape. Works for Pointlight and Spotlight.
PropertyValues: Values of the properties defined in the static structure. Use FLiveLinkBaseStaticData.FindPropertyValue to evaluate.
